1. MVP

As a till user
I want to input an item and a quantity
So the buyer can clearly see how many of each item has been bought

As a till user
I want the till to calculate the total value
So I know the value of all items purchased

As a till user
I want to the till to calculate the taxable amount
So I know how much to add on top of the total

As a till user
I want the till to calculate the total price including tax
So I know exactly how much to charge the buyer


2.

As a till user
I want the till to produce the date
So the buyer knows exactly when they purchased their goods

As a till user
I want the till to produce the name, location and phone number
So that the buyer knows the details of the coffee shop

.....


OBJECTS:
user
till
order
receipt
